    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITEDFIRST\nте п и",
      "TO BEGIN\nChilled antipasto plate\nProsciutto, coppa ham with black pepper, mozzarella cheese,\noven-roasted beets, artichokes and Kalamata olives\nMAIN COURSE\nDeluxe American cheeseburger\nLettuce, tomato, onion and a dill pickle\nCorn crumbled chicken breast stuffed with Pepper Jack cheese\nTomatillo sauce, zucchini and brown rice with beans and peppers\nThe above entrees are accompanied by heartland field greens\nwith carrots and bell peppers and balsamic vinaigrette\nor classic Caesar dressing\nPortobello stuffed Gnocchi with basil cream sauce\nToasted pine nuts and shredded Parmesan cheese\nDESSERT\nIce cream with sundae toppings\nFEATURED WINES\nYour flight attendant will inform you of today's selections.\nSparkling Wine\nVeuve Amiot Brut\nBouvet non-vintage, Loire\nWhite Wine\nGuenoc Valley California Chardonnay 2000\nPionero Valle Central Chardonnay 1999\nRed Wine\nCarmen Valle Central Cabernet Sauvignon\nLouis M. Martini California Cabernet Sauvignon 1999\n12/02\nTRANSCON (L01)\n103D002-4\n7003.009.001"
    ],
